      "provisions": [
        {
          "provision_label_raw": "section",
          "text": "The DMU zone is located in the Downtown Periphery area surrounding much of the downtown core. The area supports a range of mixed uses including mixed groundfloor es like commercial, office and residential with a mix of uses on the upper floors. The lot fabric in these areas is generally narrow with less height.",
